Interested in a career in marketing?  P&G is a world leader in marketing and talent development.  Did you know P&G invented the concept of brand, brand management, and even the Soap Opera (originally designed to showcase our soap powders on TV)?  Over the years, we've consistently remained on the cutting edge of marketing, always finding new and exciting ways of reaching consumers.  So, it's not surprising that some of the world's best marketing pros started here. Three billion times a day, P&G brands touch the lives of people around the world.
